node.text:
.
.
.
Ingredients:
1 lb strawberries sliced
1.5 cups sweetener
2 tbsp lemon juice
.
.
Instructions:
1. Add your strawberries to a sauce pan on medium heat and mix in the sugar. 
2. Stir until you bring the strawberries to a boil.
3. Once boiling add your lemon juice. 
4. Let boil for another 15 minutes / until jam reaches 220F stirring often so the jam doesn’t burn. 
5. Pour into a jar and let cool. 
.
.
#keto #ketorecipes #lowcarb #strawberries

node.text:
.
.
.
The Ellas Flats are such a bussin keto friendly option when you’re craving something light & crunchy 🙌 I highly reccomend you go order some! The link is in my bio 👍
.
.
Ingredients:
1/4 cup allulose 
2 TBSP butter
4-5 Ellas flats (link in bio)
1 tsp vanilla extract
1/8 tsp salt
.
.
Instructions:
1. Combine all ingredients except the flats in a non stick skillet over medium heat until the sweetener dissolves.
2. Add Flats and stir for 2-3 minutes.
3. Remove from stove and pour into a rimmed baking sheet / Pan lined with parchment paper. Spread peanuts evenly with a spoon. (Be careful it’s very hot)
4. Allow to cool for 1 hour. Break up into 4 servings and enjoy!
.
.
#keto #lowcarb #ketosnacks #ketotreats #ellasflats

node.text:
.
.
.
Ingredients:
1 can of chicken
1 large egg
1/2 cup shredded cheese
Seasonings of choice 
.
.
Instructions:
1. Mash your chicken up in a bowl and mix with all ingredients. 
2. Shape into nuggets and air fry on parchment paper at 400F for 8-10 minutes flipping halfway through.
3. Let cool & enjoy!
.
.
Notes: You can also bake at 400F for 20 mins flipping halfway.
.
.
#keto #lowcarb #ketorecipes

node.title: Say “YES” if you would eat these ZERO CARB CHICKEN NUGGETS 😋🙌

Ham
Cheddar 
Egg
Butter
.
.

2. Whisk your egg in a bowl. 
3. Add your ham and cheddar between both slices of bread and dip in egg wash. 
4. Pan fry in butter until golden brown on both sides. Enjoy!

Say “YES” if you would eat these Crispy Brussels Sprouts 😋

Leave a “🤢” if you hate Brussels sprouts!!

Just mix a bag of Brussels sprouts (halved) with olive or avocado oil, salt, pepper, & sweetener. Then air fry at 400F for 10 minutes. Enjoy!

#keto #lowcarb #ketorecipes

node.text:
.
.
.
Ingredients:
1 lb strawberries sliced
1.5 cups sweetener
2 tbsp lemon juice
.
.
Instructions:
1. Add your strawberries to a sauce pan on medium heat and mix in the sugar. 
2. Stir until you bring the strawberries to a boil.
3. Once boiling add your lemon juice. 
4. Let boil for another 15 minutes / until jam reaches 220F stirring often so the jam doesn’t burn. 
5. Pour into a jar and let cool. 
.
.
#keto #ketorecipes #lowcarb #strawberries

Say “YES” if you would eat these breakfast cups! 😋🙌

Ingredients:
6 slices of ham
1/2 cup shredded cheese
6 large eggs
Seasonings of your preference 

Instructions:
1. Preheat oven to 360F 
2. Add your ham to a non stick muffin tin.
3. Sprinkle in your cheese, top with an egg and your seasonings.
4. Bake for 10-15 minutes.

#keto #lowcarb #ketorecipes

node.text:
Say “YES” if you would eat these chicken finger mozzarella sticks 😋🙌

Ingredients:
Cheese sticks
Fresh chicken tenderloins 
Pork rinds
Large egg

Simply freeze your mozzarella sticks, stuff them into your chicken, coat with egg and pork rinds and air fry at 400F for 10-12 mins! It’s that easy! 👌

#keto #lowcarb #ketorecipes

node.text:
Say “YES” if you would eat this chaffle bun pizza burger 🙌🍕🍔😋

To make it just mix 1 egg with 1/2 cup mozzarella and your favorite seasonings. Then add it to the waffle maker with pepperonis sandwiched between the mix and take it out when the light comes on. Repeat, add your burger & whatever else you want, and enjoy! 

#keto #lowcarb #ketodiet #lowcarbdiet #ketorecipes #chaffle
